WEBVTT

00:01:28.382 --> 00:01:33.687
And over time, I grew less and less sure
that I actually wanted to.

00:01:34.740 --> 00:01:39.344
Therefore, the day those black corduroy
bell-bottom pants came into my life,

00:01:39.368 --> 00:01:40.688
something happened.

00:01:41.227 --> 00:01:42.624
I didn't see pants;

00:01:43.063 --> 00:01:44.564
I saw opportunity.

00:01:45.087 --> 00:01:47.788
The very next day,
I had to wear them to school,

00:01:47.812 --> 00:01:48.962
come what may.

00:01:49.820 --> 00:01:53.256
And once I pulled on those god-awful pants
and belted them tight,

00:01:53.844 --> 00:01:58.240
almost instantly, I developed
what can only be called a swagger.

00:01:58.264 --> 00:01:59.896
(Laughter)

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.586
All the way to school,